{"TopicId":128004,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"BB-8","CreatedByName":"gag09","CreatedById":57494,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-16T23:45:33Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"gag09","CreatedById":57494,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-16T23:45:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust curious has anyone made a stock version of BB-8 from starwars in KSP?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-12-16T23:51:02Z\u0022 title=\u002212/16/2015 11:51  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 16, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by gag09\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CommanderCoye","CreatedById":143167,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-17T04:40:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI expected more...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"gag09","CreatedById":57494,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-17T06:26:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo did I.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"War Eagle 1","CreatedById":67109,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-19T01:17:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKinda hard to do a stock rolling\u00A0ball with a head on top\u003Cbr\u003E\nHeres his grandpa though\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/KnXFGqV.png\u0022 alt=\u0022KnXFGqV.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-12-19T01:22:35Z\u0022 title=\u002212/19/2015 01:22  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 19, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by War Eagle 1\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Optimist","CreatedById":151904,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-19T01:26:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222328506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022128004\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221450487858\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002267109\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022War Eagle 1\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 minutes ago, War Eagle 1 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKinda hard to do a stock rolling\u00A0ball with a head on top\u003Cbr\u003E\nHeres his grandpa though\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/KnXFGqV.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022KnXFGqV.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/KnXFGqV.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAyyyy lmao\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Majorjim!","CreatedById":61954,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-19T03:46:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think I know how to make this. It will almost certainly not work but I will give it a go.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"katateochi","CreatedById":35181,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-20T19:36:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot stock, but I\u0027ve just made a working prototype with infernal robotics to drive it. \u00A0Aside from IR the main parts are stock, just tweak-scaled to be smaller. \u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022PvLQwqQ.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022624\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/PvLQwqQ.jpg\u0022 style=\u0022width:600px;height:372px;\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nquick vid -\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://youtu.be/leKjUsOQNJU\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://youtu.be/leKjUsOQNJU\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0| craft file -\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022http://kerbalx.com/katateochi/BB-8\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://kerbalx.com/katateochi/BB-8\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"gag09","CreatedById":57494,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-20T23:41:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAmazing. I am at a loss for words.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Yukon0009","CreatedById":109376,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-21T02:16:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA very basic version\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i1383.photobucket.com/albums/ah315/Yukon0009/screenshot7405_zpsizd9dz5t.png\u0022 alt=\u0022screenshot7405_zpsizd9dz5t.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BagelRabbit","CreatedById":95028,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-21T23:00:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlright. I tried to make a BB-8 droid yesterday.\u00A0After a \u003Cem\u003Elot\u003C/em\u003E of unsuccessful testing, I present to you the best result I ended up achieving:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/i9dobpd.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022i9dobpd.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis BB-8 \u003Cem\u003Ecan\u003C/em\u003E move (it has hidden wheels on the bottom) but it doesn\u0027t like inclines or braking too quickly. Nevertheless, it\u0027s completely stock and I think it\u0027s a suitable representation of the droid.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf yeh like it, I could probably deliver a .craft file (though not right now; I can\u0027t access KSP at the moment).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-Upsilon\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sgt_flyer","CreatedById":57690,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-22T01:22:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nfun \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E here\u0027s a BB8 full stock \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E (which actually uses it\u0027s ball for moving :p)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/gMBUaSy\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022gMBUaSyl.png?1\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/gMBUaSyl.png?1\u0022 style=\u0022width:636px;height:398px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhere\u0027s a small gif of it (low quality) : \u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/rW8Tgyw\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://imgur.com/rW8Tgyw\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOperations :\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nengage SAS, then stage once to separate the \u0027head\u0027 from the ball \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E (you\u0027ll know on which part you\u0027ll be when switching vessel, the \u0027head\u0027 as nothing in staging, while the \u0027ball\u0027 has the decoupler and the fairing in it\u0027s list \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E )\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nswitch to the ball if necessary, disable the SAS on the ball, and trim roll to the maximum right (alt\u002BQ by default)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nswitch back to the \u0027head\u0027, and you can adjust it\u0027s course as necessary \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E (W / S controls the head\u0027s angle around the white part, Q / E allows you to go left / right, A / D allows you to tilt on the side \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nfor stopping, switch back to the ball, and kill the trim (alt\u002BX by default), and BB8 will stop \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nroughly 5 m/s of speed on flat surface, and can climb up KSC\u0027s slopes at around 4m/s \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(as an added bonus, the head tend to tilt a bit forward on it\u0027s own when it\u0027s moving :p)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www./download/icfzot7bzff8cf9/bb8.craft\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://www./download/icfzot7bzff8cf9/bb8.craft\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-12-22T01:27:14Z\u0022 title=\u002212/22/2015 01:27  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 22, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by sgt_flyer\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Majorjim!","CreatedById":61954,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-22T02:35:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-conten